                "author": {
                  "login": "ConcaveTrillion"
                },
                "body": "Tracking issue — workarounds are confirmed in place:\n1. Page.merge_words: SPA spec-23-C2 uses page.lines[line_index].merge_word_left/right directly (the per-line API is the natural fit for the current per-word endpoint).\n2. Page.erase_pixels: SPA mutates page.cv2_numpy_page_image in place + calls page.finalize_page_structure() — same shape as legacy labeler.\nRe-open if a collective endpoint is added to the SPA in a future milestone.",
